            <title>[LOG4J2-1363] includeLocation doesn&apos;t work when using PropertiesConfiguration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1363</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using AsyncLoggerContextSelector, the default value of the includeLocation is false. &lt;br/&gt;
This can be changed by setting &quot;includeLocation=true&quot; in the configuration of the relevant loggers.&lt;br/&gt;
But it doesn&apos;t work when using properties as the configuration, because the method of createRootLogger in PropertiesConfiguration ignores the includeLocation issues which causing no lineNum shows&lt;/p&gt;</description>
